    "description": "Kitchen Trials: Rush is a speed-based 2D platformer where you have to get to the end of each stage as quickly as possible with your speed determining whether you pass this trial and make it one step closer to joining the most elusive and renowned kitchen. You are a promising candidate who uses a set of kitchen knives attached to a chain to whip through each stage chopping through any living vegetables encountered. You'll have to be fast to catch the proctor's riffling eyes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2>- Attach to various enemies and pull them towards you to chop them into pieces as you speed through.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/7a42afed8618b863640b37988c6e087c.poster.avif?t=1736530080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/7a42afed8618b863640b37988c6e087c.webm?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/7a42afed8618b863640b37988c6e087c.mp4?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- When facing larger veggies pull yourself towards them to swing through the stages at high speeds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/04313d72db5b31550e01719793d24028.poster.avif?t=1736530080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/04313d72db5b31550e01719793d24028.webm?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/04313d72db5b31550e01719793d24028.mp4?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Finish stages as fast as possible to impress your proctor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/eddcccfa061dabb7e736f48cbbc0de8b.poster.avif?t=1736530080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/eddcccfa061dabb7e736f48cbbc0de8b.webm?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132110/extras/eddcccfa061dabb7e736f48cbbc0de8b.mp4?t=1736530080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
